  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A right rectangular prism has a base area of <math alttext=\"24 t square centimeters left parenthesis c m squared right parenthesis\"><mn>24</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>square</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>centimeters</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mfenced><msup><mi>cm</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfenced></math>. The length of the base of the rectangular prism is <math alttext=\"eight thirds c m\"><mfrac><mn>8</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>cm</mi></math>, and the height of the rectangular prism is <math alttext=\"15 c m\"><mn>15</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>cm</mi></math>. Which expression represents the surface area, in <math alttext=\"c m squared\"><msup><mi>cm</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, of the right rectangular prism?</p>",
